### Create Prompt Group
This endpoint allows the creation of a new prompt group.

- Method: POST
- URL: `{{BASE_URL}}/llmpromptgroups/`

#### Request Body
- Type: JSON
    - `Name`: (string) The name of the prompt group.
    - `Description`: (string) A brief description of the prompt group.

#### Response
The response of this request is a JSON schema representing the structure of the created prompt group.

Example:
```json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "id": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "Name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "Description": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "createdAt": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time"
        },
        "updatedAt": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time"
        }
    }
}
```
